   Schwind, Christopher; Thompson, John N., Univ Calif Santa Cruz, Dept Ecol \& Evolutionary Biol, Santa Cruz, CA 95060 USA.
   Guimaraes, Paulo R., Jr., Univ Sao Paulo, Inst Biociencias, Dept Ecol, BR-05508090 Sao Paulo, Brazil.
